Package: localintel
Type: Package
Title: Local Intelligence - Subnational Data Pipeline for 150+ Eurostat Regional Indicators
Version: 0.2.1
Authors@R: person("Mohamed", "Htitich", 
                  email = "m.ahtitich@outlook.com", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-8732-6286"))
Description: A comprehensive pipeline for fetching, harmonizing, cascading, and
    visualizing 150+ subnational indicators from Eurostat across 14 thematic domains
    including economy, health, education, labour market, demographics, tourism,
    transport, environment, science and technology, agriculture, poverty, business
    statistics, information society, and crime. Provides NUTS 0/1/2 data cascading
    with source-level tracking, composite scoring, publication-ready maps, and
    Tableau-ready exports for 235+ European NUTS-2 regions.
